{{> app/template/partial/site-header }}

<div class="o-scroll" data-module-scroll="main">
    <section data-scroll-section>
        <header class="c-header -difference">
            {{> app/template/partial/header }}
        </header>
        <div class="c-section">
            <div class="o-container">
                <header class="c-header-contact">
                    <div class="o-layout -gutter">
                        <div class="o-layout_item u-3/5@from-medium">
                            <h1 class="c-heading -h1 u-color-blue">
                                Get in touch
                            </h1>
                            <p class="c-header-contact_infos">
                                Lorem ipsum dolor <br> consectetur adipisicing elit.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="o-layout_item u-2/5@from-medium">
                            <h2 class="c-heading -h4">
                                Your message
                            </h2>
                            <form 
                                class="c-header-contact_form"
                                action="" 
                                data-module-form
                                data-form-confirm-message="Thank you! Our team will reach out as soon as possible."
                                data-form-error-message="Error message"
                                >
                                <div class="o-layout -gutter">
                                    <div class="o-layout_item u-1/2@from-small">
                                        <div class="c-form_item">
                                            <label class="c-form_label" for="first-name">First name</label>
                                            <input type="text" class="c-form_input" id="first-name" name="first-name">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="o-layout_item u-1/2@from-small">
                                        <div class="c-form_item">
                                            <label class="c-form_label" for="last-name">Last name</label>
                                            <input type="text" class="c-form_input" id="last-name" name="last-name">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="o-layout_item">
                                        <div class="c-form_item">
                                            <label class="c-form_label" for="e-mail">E-mail</label>
                                            <input type="e-mail" class="c-form_input" id="e-mail" name="e-mail">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="o-layout_item">
                                        <div class="c-form_item">
                                            <label class="c-form_label" for="message">Message</label>
                                            <textarea name="message" class="c-form_textarea" id="message"></textarea>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="o-layout_item u-1/2" data-form="feedback">
                                        
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="o-layout_item u-1/2 u-text-right">
                                        <div class="c-header-contact_submit_wrap">
                                            <div class="c-spinner">
                                                <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true"><use href="assets/images/sprite.svg#spinner"></use></svg>
                                            </div>
                                            <button class="c-header-contact_submit c-button -blue -big">
                                                See live
                                            </button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </header>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section data-scroll-section>
        <div class="c-section">
            <div class="o-container">
                <div class="o-layout -gutter-huge">
                    <div class="o-layout_item u-1/3@from-medium">
                        <div class="c-wysiwyg">
                            <p class="c-heading -h3">So you’re about to make a crucial decision between using Charcoal, WordPress or Drupal for the development of your next digital project?</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="o-layout_item u-1/2@from-small u-1/3@from-large">
                        <div class="c-wysiwyg">
                            <p>Let us guide you through the benefits of a modern development framework like Charcoal and let’s compare with the best-in-class such as WordPress or Drupal. Our comprehensive guide will help you understand what makes Charcoal stand out from other trusted content management platforms and when you should consider implementing Charcoal into your digital project.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="o-layout_item u-1/2@from-small u-1/3@from-large">
                        <div class="c-wysiwyg">
                            <p>Built for those who are aspiring to offer only the best user experiences without compromises or limitations, Charcoal will make (almost) all of your dreams come true with a user-friendly and multi-device interface to manage your Website, power your eCommerce, control your Messaging platform and crunch your Data. It is open-source, performant, W3C compliant and secure.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

{{> app/template/partial/site-footer }}